{
 "name": "RPlog_Morganna_in_Love",
 "title": "Morganna in Love",
 "summary": "In the lounge of the station Guardian, the scarred Morganna broods at the viewport while the sinister, cold-aura captain Atrox glides among the patrons, and Admiral Adlerson arrives all but glowing with an unspoken, lovestruck cheer toward her. When a firefight flares just outside the station, Atrox secretly launches a squadron of eerily hypnotic Interceptors, and Adlerson and Morganna discuss her imminent departure from Imperial space now that her spice detox is complete. Adlerson, plainly smitten though concealing it behind military reserve, secures her promise to stay clean and to pass along his regards, and the two part warmly. Morganna settles by the viewport as Atrox unwraps his ritual bottle of wine and the newcomer Hawke drifts in.",
